author: max
name: EmojiSpam
install_msg:
Thanks for installing.
This cog relies on red's autoimmune, to ignore role(s) or user(s) use `[p]autoimmune` from red. You are not immune from any Emoji spam filter without setting up autoimmune.
description: Similar emojispam filter to dyno but without ban, kick and mute.
short: Similar emojispam filter to dyno but without ban, kick and mute.
end_user_data_statement: This cog does not store any End User Data.
